question: Show me the top three most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed within the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with hypertrophy (benign) of prostate without urinary obstruction and other lower urinary tract symptom (luts) this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypertrophy (benign) of prostate without urinary obstruction and other lower urinary tract symptom (luts)' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

generated_sql: SELECT MIN(created_at) FROM patient_vitals WHERE patient_id = 10018081 AND created_at >= '2023-04-10' AND respiratory_rate < 23.0

question: Which were the three most commonly ordered procedures for patients previously diagnosed with streptococcus infection in conditions classified elsewhere and of unspecified site, streptococcus, group d [enterococcus] during the same month, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'streptococcus infection in conditions classified elsewhere and of unspecified site, streptococcus, group d [enterococcus]' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 3 procedure, COUNT(*) as count FROM patient_records WHERE diagnosis = 'Streptococcus infection, conditions classified elsewhere and of unspecified site' AND conditions = 'Streptococcus, group D Enterococcus

question: On the current hospital visit, how many hours have passed since patient 10018081's first diagnosis of abnormal coagulation profile?

question: Name the three most frequently prescribed drugs in the same hospital visit following a diagnosis of pure hypercholesterolemia.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'pure hypercholesterolemia' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT drugs.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM hospital_visits JOIN diagnoses ON hospital_visits.visit_id = diagnoses.visit_id JOIN drug_prescriptions ON hospital_visits.visit_id = drug_prescriptions.visit_id WHERE diagnoses.condition = 'Pure hypercholesterolemia' GROUP BY drugs.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3

question: Provide a list of the four most common diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after undergoing the extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS count FROM diagnoses d JOIN procedures p ON d.patient_id = p.patient_id WHERE p.procedure_name = 'Extirpation of matter from right lower lung lobe via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure' AND d.diagnosis_date BETWEEN p.procedure_date AND DATE_ADD(p.procedure_date, INTERVAL 2 MONTH) GROUP BY d.diagnosis ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 4

question: What are the five most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were diagnosed with atherosclerotic heart disease of native coronary artery without angina pectoris previously in the same month, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atherosclerotic heart disease of native coronary artery without angina pectoris' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT DISTINCT t1.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS count FROM prescriptions t1 JOIN diagnoses t2 ON t1.patient_id = t2.patient_id WHERE t1.month = 2100 AND t2.condition = 'atherosclerotic heart disease of native coronary artery without angina pectoris' AND t2.month = 2100 GROUP BY t1.drug_name ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 5

question: What is the treatment that patient 10007795 was given two or more times since 23 months ago?

question: What are the three most common diagnoses of patients in their 30s this year?

question: What are the five commonly ordered medications that patients aged 60 or above were prescribed in the same month after diagnosed with retention of urine, unspecified in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'retention of urine, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT t1.medication_name, COUNT(*) as prescriptions FROM patient_data t1 JOIN diagnosis_data t2 ON t1.patient_id = t2.patient_id WHERE t2.diagnosis_code = 'N309' AND t1.age >= 60 AND MONTH(t1.prescription_date) = MONTH('2100-01-01') AND YEAR(t1.prescription_date) = YEAR('2100-01-01') GROUP BY t1.medication_name ORDER BY prescriptions DESC LIMIT 5

question: What are the three most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were previously diagnosed with grand mal status within the same month, this year?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'grand mal status' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT medication_name, COUNT(*) as prescription_count FROM prescriptions INNER JOIN patients ON prescriptions.patient_id = patients.id WHERE patients.previous_diagnosis = 'grand mal status' AND DATE_FORMAT(prescriptions.prescription_date, '%Y-%m') = DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m') GROUP BY medication_name ORDER BY prescription_count DESC LIMIT 3

question: List the top four most frequent microbiology tests that were given to patients after they were diagnosed with sepsis during the same hospital visit during this year.
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'sepsis' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: For patients who received performance of cardiac output, continuous , what are the top five most frequent diagnoses that followed afterwards within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'performance of cardiac output, continuous' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT patient_id) FROM procedures WHERE procedure_code = '38.47' AND month(procedure_date) = month(diagnosis_date) AND diagnosis_code LIKE 'E87.0%' AND misadventure_at_time_of_procedure = 'No'

question: Tell me the name of the drug which patient 10021487 was prescribed within 2 days after having had a closed [endoscopic] biopsy of bronchus procedure since 9 months ago?

question: In 2100, how many patients underwent a venous catheterization, not elsewhere classified in the same month after the diagnosis of hepatic encephalopathy?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hepatic encephalopathy' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'venous catheterization, not elsewhere classified' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')
generated_sql: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.patient_num) FROM patient p INNER JOIN encounter e ON p.patient_num = e.patient_num INNER JOIN diagnosis d ON e.encounter_num = d.encounter_num INNER JOIN procedure pr ON e.encounter_num = pr.encounter_num WHERE d.diagnosis_code = 'K72.0' AND pr.procedure_code = '99.70' AND YEAR(e.admit_date) = 2100 AND MONTH(e.admit_date) = MONTH(d.diagnosis_date) AND MONTH(e.admit_date) = MONTH(pr.proc_date )

question: What are the four most regularly ordered treatments for patients previously diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis in the same hospital visit in 2100?

question: Show me the top four diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate.

question: What was the last time that patient 10022041 was prescribed acetaminophen iv and phosphorus in 06/2100, at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'acetaminophen iv' AND admissions.subject_id = 10022041 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-06' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phosphorus' AND admissions.subject_id = 10022041 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-06' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT date FROM prescription WHERE patient = '10022041' AND drug = 'acetaminophen iv' AND date = ( SELECT date FROM prescription WHERE patient = '10022041' AND drug = 'phosphorus' AND date LIKE '06/2100%' ) LIMIT 1

question: When was the first time patient 10008287 had an maximum po2 in their first hospital visit?

question: In 2100, what are the top four most frequent medications prescribed during the same month to the patients in their 60 or above after they were diagnosed with atrial fibrillation?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atrial fibrillation' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 4 m.medicine_name, COUNT(m.medicine_name) AS frequency FROM patient_data p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id JOIN medication m ON p.patient_id = m.patient_id WHERE d.disease_name = 'atrial_fibrillation' AND p.age >= 60 AND YEAR(m.prescription_date) = 2010 AND MONTH(m.prescription_date) = 12 GROUP BY m.medicine_name ORDER BY frequency DESC

question: How many hours have passed since patient 10018081 last received a laboratory test of calculated total co2 in this hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT 24 * ( strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J', labevents.charttime) ) FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'calculated total co2' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018081 AND admissions.dischtime IS NULL ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT DATEDIFF(HOUR, MAX(lab_order_dt_tm), CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) AS hours_since_last_co2_test FROM labs WHERE patient_id = '10018081' AND lab_test_name = 'CALCULATED TOTAL CO2' AND visit_id = ( SELECT visit_id FROM visits WHERE patient_id = '10018081' )

question: When heparin and aspirin were prescribed to patient 10016150 for the last time in 05/this year at the same time?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'heparin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10016150 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'aspirin' AND admissions.subject_id = 10016150 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '05' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime DESC LIMIT 1
generated_sql: SELECT T2.encounternumber , T2.drug , MAX ( T2.endtime ) FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT T1.encounternumber , T1.drug , T1.starttime , T1.endtime FROM ( SELECT encounternumber , drug , MIN ( starttime ) AS starttime , MAX ( endtime ) AS endtime FROM `prescribed` WHERE ( drug IN ( 'heparin' , 'aspirin' ) ) GROUP BY encounternumber , drug ) T1 INNER JOIN ( SELECT encounternumber , drug FROM `prescribed` WHERE drug IN ( 'heparin' , 'aspirin' ) GROUP BY encounternumber , drug HAVING COUNT ( DISTINCT starttime ) = 1 ) T3 ON T1.encounternumber = T3.encounternumber AND T1.drug = T3.drug WHERE T1.endtime = '05/2022' AND T1.encounternumber = '10016150' GROUP BY T1.encounternumber , T1.drug

question: What are the four most common diagnoses for patients who previously had the dilation of right main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic procedure within 2 months since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'dilation of right main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT Diagnosis, COUNT(*) AS Count FROM PatientDiagnosis WHERE Procedure = 'dilation of right main bronchus with intraluminal device, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' AND Date BETWEEN DATEADD(year, -1, GETDATE()) AND DATEADD(month, -2, GETDATE()) GROUP BY Diagnosis ORDER BY Count DESC LIMIT 4

question: Calculate patient 10029484's total input amount of magnesium sulfate (bolus) on last month/23.

question: What are the five most typically ordered procedures for patients previously diagnosed with other symbolic dysfunction, which took place within 2 months in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other symbolic dysfunction' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: What are the three most frequently prescribed drugs in the same hospital encounter to the patients aged 40s after they were diagnosed with acute embolism and thrombosis of left iliac vein in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute embolism and thrombosis of left iliac vein' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: What are the five most frequently ordered medications that patients in their 30s were prescribed during the same month after being diagnosed with unspecified essential hypertension in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified essential hypertension' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Can you get me the top four diagnoses that have the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.diagnosis_name, (COUNT(CASE WHEN m.mortality_outcome = 'Yes' THEN 1 END) / COUNT(m.mortality_outcome)) * 100 AS mortality_rate FROM diagnosis d JOIN patient p ON d.patient_id = p.patient_id JOIN mortality m ON p.patient_id = m.patient_id WHERE m.mortality_timeframe = '6 months' GROUP BY d.diagnosis_name ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC LIMIT 4

question: What was the name of the drug patient 10021487 was prescribed with within the same hospital visit after having received a enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances procedure throughout this month?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021487 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of month') = datetime(current_time,'start of month','-0 month') ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime

question: What were the five most frequently ordered procedures for patients who had also received drainage of left pleural cavity, percutaneous approach within the same month this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of left pleural cavity, percutaneous approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM procedures p JOIN patients pt ON p.patient_id = pt.id WHERE p.procedure_date BETWEEN DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE) AND LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE) AND p.procedure_name LIKE 'Drainage of left pleural cavity, percutaneous approach' AND pt.id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM procedures WHERE procedure_date BETWEEN DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE) AND LAST_DAY(CURRENT_DATE)) GROUP BY p.procedure_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5

question: What are the top three most frequent drugs prescribed to patients in the same month after the diagnosis of gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM prescriptions JOIN diagnoses ON prescriptions.patient_id = diagnoses.patient_id WHERE diagnosis = 'Gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis' AND prescription_date BETWEEN diagnoses.diagnosis_date AND DATE_ADD(diagnoses.diagnosis_date, INTERVAL 1 MONTH) GROUP BY drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3

question: Can you tell me the top three diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )

question: Retrieve the top four most frequent procedures that patients were given within 2 months after receiving occlusion of right vertebral artery with intraluminal device, percutaneous approach throughout this year.

generated_sql: SELECT T1.procedure_description , COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM procedures AS T1 JOIN patients AS T2 ON T1.patient_id = T2.id WHERE T2.occlusion_date >= DATEADD(YEAR, DATEDIFF(YEAR, 0, GETDATE()), 0) AND T2.occlusion_date < DATEADD(YEAR, DATEDIFF(YEAR, 0, GETDATE()) + 1, 0) AND T2.occlusion_type = 'Right vertebral artery, occlusion with intraluminal device, percutaneous approach' AND DATEDIFF(MONTH, T2.occlusion_date, T1.procedure_date) BETWEEN 0 AND 2 GROUP BY T1.procedure_description ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4

question: What are the top three diagnoses associated with the highest 3-month mortality rate?

question: Can you provide the name of the drug that was prescribed to patient 10022017 within 2 days post bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach procedure in the last hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'bypass coronary artery, three arteries from aorta with autologous venous tissue, open approach' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10022017 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')
generated_sql: SELECT T1.DrugName FROM Medication_Orders AS T1 JOIN Patients AS T2 ON T1.PatientID = T2.PatientID WHERE T2.PatientID = '10022017' AND T2.HospitalVisitDate = ( SELECT MAX(HospitalVisitDate) FROM Patients WHERE PatientID = '10022017' ) AND T2.Diagnosis LIKE '%bypass coronary artery%' AND T2.Diagnosis LIKE '%three arteries from aorta%' AND T2.Procedure LIKE '%autologous venous tissue%' AND T2.Procedure LIKE '%open approach%' AND T1.OrderedDate BETWEEN DATEADD(DAY, -2, T2.HospitalVisitDate) AND T2.HospitalVisitDate

question: Tell me the name of the diagnosis that patient 10009035 received last since 1 year ago?

question: Provide the top four most common treatments since 1 year ago.

question: In 2100, which are the four most frequent lab tests given to patients within the same month after they are diagnosed with personal history of alcoholism?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of alcoholism' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: For patients who were previously diagnosed with fall resulting in striking against other object, what are the top four most frequent treatments in the same month since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'fall resulting in striking against other object' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT treatment_name, COUNT(*) as freq FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT patient_id, treatment_name FROM patient_records WHERE diagnosis = 'Fall resulting in striking against other object' AND date_of_service >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 1 YEAR) AND MONTH(date_of_service) = MONTH(CURDATE()) AND YEAR(date_of_service) = YEAR(CURDATE()) ) AS subquery GROUP BY treatment_name ORDER BY freq DESC LIMIT 4

question: Could you tell me the name of the drug prescribed to patient 10018081 within 2 days after the enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances procedure since 09/2100?

question: Since 2100, what are the top five most common microbiology tests that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after being diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'noncompliance with renal dialysis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 5 M.test_name , COUNT(*) AS occurrences FROM microbiology_tests M JOIN patients P ON M.patient_id = P.id WHERE P.diagnosis_date > '2100-01-01' AND M.diagnosis_date BETWEEN DATEADD(MONTH, -2, P.diagnosis_date) AND P.diagnosis_date AND P.diagnosis = 'Noncompliance with renal dialysis' GROUP BY M.test_name ORDER BY occurrences DESC

question: How many patients underwent extirpation of matter from left common iliac vein, percutaneous approach within 2 months after the diagnosis of operating room of hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause, in the last year?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'operating room of hospital as the place of occurrence of the external cause' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extirpation of matter from left common iliac vein, percutaneous approach' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month')

question: What are the three most common diagnoses for patients who previously had the excision of dental lesion of jaw procedure within 2 months since 1 year ago?

generated_sql: SELECT Diagnosis, COUNT(*) as occurrences FROM patient_records WHERE Procedure = 'Excision of dental lesion of jaw' AND (Date_of_Procedure BETWEEN NOW() - INTERVAL 1 YEAR AND NOW() - INTERVAL 2 MONTH) GROUP BY Diagnosis ORDER BY occurrences DESC LIMIT 3;

question: Among patients who were given closed [percutaneous] [needle] biopsy of kidney , what are the top five most common specimens tested afterward within 2 months?

generated_sql: SELECT T2."Specimen Name" , COUNT(*) AS count FROM i2b2public."2100" AS T1 JOIN i2b2public."Specimens 2100" AS T2 ON T1."Encounter ID" = T2."Encounter ID" WHERE T1."Procedure Description" = 'Destruction of right lower lung lobe, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' AND T1."Encounter ID" = T2."Encounter ID" GROUP BY T2."Specimen Name" ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 4

question: Can you tell me the top four most common treatments for patients in their 30s?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 ) GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT treatment, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patients JOIN treatments ON patients.patient_id = treatments.patient_id WHERE patients.age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 GROUP BY treatment ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4

question: Get me the top five most frequent procedures that patients received within 2 months after receiving closed [endoscopic] biopsy of bronchus since 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'closed [endoscopic] biopsy of bronchus' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 5 procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT patient_id, procedure_name FROM procedures WHERE procedure_date >= DATEADD(month, -2, (SELECT MAX(procedure_date) FROM procedures WHERE procedure_name = 'Closed Endoscopic Biopsy of Bronchus')) AND procedure_name != 'Closed Endoscopic Biopsy of Bronchus' ) AS subquery GROUP BY procedure_name ORDER BY frequency DESC

question: What is the difference between mean blood pressure on patient 10002495 last measured on the last ICU visit compared to the value second to last measured on the last ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )
generated_sql: WITH last_icu AS ( SELECT icustay_id, admissionid, admission_dt, discharge_dt FROM icustays WHERE subject_id = 10002495 ORDER BY admission_dt DESC LIMIT 1 ) , last_bp AS ( SELECT last_icu.*, c.icustay_id, c.charttime, c.valuenum FROM last_icu JOIN chartevents AS c ON last_icu.icustay_id = c.icustay_id WHERE c.itemid = 220175 AND c.charttime BETWEEN last_icu.admission_dt AND last_icu.discharge_dt ORDER BY c.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) , second_last_bp AS ( SELECT last_bp.* FROM last_bp JOIN chartevents AS c ON last_bp.icustay_id = c.icustay_id WHERE c.itemid = 220175 AND c.charttime BETWEEN last_bp.admission_dt AND last_bp.discharge_dt AND c.charttime < last_bp.charttime ORDER BY c.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) SELECT last_bp.valuenum - second_last_bp.valuenum AS difference FROM last_bp, second_last_bp
true_result: [{"( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure mean' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )": None}]

question: What are the four most commonly prescribed medications for patients who were diagnosed with facial weakness previously within 2 months, in 2100?

question: Retrieve the top five most frequent procedures that patients were given during the same hospital encounter after receiving inspection of tracheobronchial tree, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic in 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'inspection of tracheobronchial tree, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT p1.procedure_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM procedures p1 JOIN encounters e ON p1.encounter_id = e.id WHERE p1.procedure_date = '2100-01-01' AND e.inspection_procedure = 'Inspection of tracheobronchial tree, via natural or artificial opening (endoscopic)' GROUP BY p1.procedure_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5

question: What were the top three most common procedures in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T1.icd_code FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT procedure_name, COUNT(*) as occurrences FROM procedures WHERE year = 2100 GROUP BY procedure_name ORDER BY occurrences DESC LIMIT 3

question: What was the last time when patient 10006580 received a creatinine lab test since 03/2100?
true_query: SELECT labevents.charttime FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'creatinine' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10006580 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',labevents.charttime) >= '2100-03' ORDER BY labevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Show me the top three most commonly prescribed drugs since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT T1.drug FROM ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM prescriptions WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY prescriptions.drug ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT drug_name, COUNT(*) AS prescription_count FROM prescriptions WHERE prescription_date > DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 1 YEAR) GROUP BY drug_name ORDER BY prescription_count DESC LIMIT 3

question: In 2100, what are the top four most common specimens tested for patients previously diagnosed with obstructive chronic bronchitis with (acute) exacerbation within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'obstructive chronic bronchitis with (acute) exacerbation' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT top 4 specimen_name FROM patient_records WHERE diagnosis = 'obstructive chronic bronchitis with (acute) exacerbation' AND test_date BETWEEN '2099-12-01' AND '2100-11-30' GROUP BY specimen_name ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC

question: When was the last time patient 10021487 had input on this month/11?

question: Tell me the top four most frequent procedures that patients were given within 2 months after receiving excision of left main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic since 2100.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'excision of left main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT P2.procedure_name , COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM Patient P JOIN Procedure P1 ON P.patient_id = P1.patient_id AND P1.procedure_date BETWEEN P1.procedure_date AND DATE_ADD(P1.procedure_date, INTERVAL 2 MONTH) JOIN Procedure P2 ON P.patient_id = P2.patient_id AND P2.procedure_date BETWEEN P1.procedure_date AND DATE_ADD(P1.procedure_date, INTERVAL 2 MONTH) WHERE P1.procedure_name = 'Excision of left main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic, diagnostic' AND P1.procedure_date >= '2100-01-01' GROUP BY P2.procedure_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4

question: Tell me the time when patient 10020187's mean blood pressure was less than 91.0 for the first time on 02/03/this year?

question: What was the name of the drug patient 10017492 was prescribed within the same hospital visit after having received a spinal tap procedure in 03/this year?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'spinal tap' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10017492 ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',procedures_icd.charttime) = '03' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10017492 ) AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '03' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime
generated_sql: SELECT T1.DRUG FROM (SELECT DRUG, ENCOUNTER FROM drug_orders WHERE PATIENT = '10017492' AND PROCEDURE = 'Spinal Tap' AND YEAR(DATE) = YEAR(CURDATE()) AND MONTH(DATE) = 3) AS T1 JOIN (SELECT ENCOUNTER FROM drug_orders WHERE PATIENT = '10017492' AND PROCEDURE = 'Spinal Tap' AND YEAR(DATE) = YEAR(CURDATE()) AND MONTH(DATE) = 3) AS T2 ON T1.ENCOUNTER = T2.ENCOUNTER WHERE T1.DRUG IS NOT NULL AND T2.DRUG IS NOT NULL

question: When was the first time that patient 10038081 since 136 days ago had a respiratory rate that was less than 14.0?

question: Reveal the four most frequently prescribed medications since 1 year ago.

question: What were the top four most common diagnoses that followed within 2 months for those who received enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'enteral infusion of concentrated nutritional substances' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )
generated_sql: SELECT d FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT dx AS d, COUNT(dx) AS count FROM diagnoses JOIN admissions ON diagnoses.admission_id = admissions.id WHERE admissions.icd9_code = '2100' AND diagnoses.timestamp <= admissions.timestamp + INTERVAL '2' MONTH GROUP BY dx ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 4 ) subquery

question: List the top three most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within 2 months after receiving respiratory ventilation, greater than 96 consecutive hours.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'respiratory ventilation, greater than 96 consecutive hours' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT diagnosis, COUNT(*) as frequency FROM diagnoses JOIN ventilations ON diagnoses.patient_id = ventilations.patient_id WHERE ventilations.duration_hours > 96 AND diagnoses.timestamp BETWEEN ventilations.timestamp AND DATE_ADD(ventilations.timestamp, INTERVAL 2 MONTH) GROUP BY diagnosis ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3

question: What is the percentile ranking of a glucose test value of 176.0 for patients of the same age as patient 10038992 on the last hospital visit?

question: Could you list the three most frequently prescribed medicines in the same month after a diagnosis of coronary atherosclerosis of native coronary artery was made since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'coronary atherosclerosis of native coronary artery' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: For patients who were previously diagnosed with backache, unspecified, what are the top four most frequent treatments within 2 months since 1 year ago?

question: Retrieve the top four most frequent procedures that were delivered to patients within the same hospital visit after they received other endovascular procedures on other vessels.

generated_sql: WITH filtered_procedures AS ( SELECT hospitalization, procedure FROM endovascular_procedures WHERE procedure_code LIKE '%933%' ), same_visit_procedures AS ( SELECT ep1.hospitalization, ep1.procedure AS first_procedure, ep2.procedure AS subsequent_procedure FROM filtered_procedures ep1 JOIN endovascular_procedures ep2 ON ep1.hospitalization = ep2.hospitalization AND ep1.procedure_id < ep2.procedure_id WHERE ep2.procedure_code NOT LIKE '%933%' ) SELECT first_procedure, COUNT(*) AS occurrences FROM same_visit_procedures GROUP BY first_procedure ORDER BY occurrences DESC LIMIT 4

question: Could you retrieve the top four diagnoses that have the highest 6-month mortality rate?

generated_sql: SELECT t1.date, t1.medication, t1.amount, t1.route, t1.frequency, t1.duration, t1.nurse, t1.prescribed_by, t1.patient_id FROM medication_changes AS t1 JOIN ( SELECT patient_id, MAX(date) - INTERVAL 1 DAY AS yesterday FROM medication_changes GROUP BY patient_id ) AS t2 ON t1.patient_id = t2.patient_id AND t1.date = CURRENT_DATE AND t2.yesterday = DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 DAY) WHERE t1.patient_id = 10018081

question: For patient 10018081, how many days have passed since the last diagnosis with urinary tract infection, site not specified on this hospital encounter?

question: What's the percentile of 18.1 in a white blood cells lab test at the same age as patient 10026354 during the first hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT DISTINCT T1.C1 FROM ( SELECT labevents.valuenum, PERCENT_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY labevents.valuenum ) AS C1 FROM labevents WHERE labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'white blood cells' ) AND labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.age = ( SELECT admissions.age FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10026354 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC LIMIT 1 ) ) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.valuenum = 18.1

question: Among patients who were diagnosed with postinflammatory pulmonary fibrosis, what were the top four most common microbiology tests conducted during the same month in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'postinflammatory pulmonary fibrosis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 4 test_name, COUNT(*) as test_count FROM patients p JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patient_id = d.patient_id JOIN microbiology_tests mt ON p.patient_id = mt.patient_id WHERE d.diagnosis = 'postinflammatory pulmonary fibrosis' AND YEAR(mt.test_date) = 2100 AND MONTH(mt.test_date) = MONTH(d.diagnosis_date) GROUP BY test_name ORDER BY test_count DESC

question: Among patients who took central venous catheter placement with guidance since 1 year ago, what are the top three most frequent diagnoses that followed within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT diagnosis FROM patient WHERE catheter_placement_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year' AND diagnosis_date BETWEEN catheter_placement_date + INTERVAL '2 months' AND catheter_placement_date + INTERVAL '2 months' + INTERVAL '1 day' GROUP BY diagnosis ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 3

question: What was the name of the medication which patient 10025463 was prescribed within 2 days after receiving other electric countershock of heart since 11/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other electric countershock of heart' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10025463 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-11' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10025463 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-11' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 day')

question: What are the three most frequently administered laboratory tests for patients previously diagnosed with nontoxic uninodular goiter within the same hospital visit, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'nontoxic uninodular goiter' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT lab_test_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patient_data WHERE diagnosis = 'nontoxic uninodular goiter' AND visit_type = 'same' AND year = 2100 GROUP BY lab_test_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3

question: What are the four most commonly prescribed medications for patients diagnosed with candidiasis of mouth previously within the same hospital visit, during this year?

generated_sql: SELECT DISTINCT TOP 4 p.name FROM procedure p JOIN procedure_occurrence po ON p.procedure_concept_id = po.procedure_concept_id JOIN condition_occurrence co ON po.person_id = co.person_id WHERE po.visit_occurrence_id = co.visit_occurrence_id AND co.condition_source_value = 'Calculus of kidney' AND po.procedure_type_concept_id = 1 GROUP BY p.name ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC

question: Can you find the three most frequent drugs that were prescribed within 2 months after a swelling, mass, or lump in head and neck diagnosis was given since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'swelling, mass, or lump in head and neck' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT t2.drug_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patients t1 JOIN prescriptions t2 ON t1.patient_id = t2.patient_id WHERE t1.date_of_diagnosis >= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 YEAR) AND t1.diagnosis IN ('Swelling, Mass, or Lump in Head and Neck') AND t2.date_prescribed BETWEEN DATE_ADD(t1.date_of_diagnosis, INTERVAL 1 MONTH) AND DATE_ADD(t1.date_of_diagnosis, INTERVAL 2 MONTHS) GROUP BY t2.drug_name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3

question: What are the five most frequently ordered medications that patients in their 50s were prescribed within 2 months after they were diagnosed with other specified procedures as the cause of abnormal reaction of patient, or of later complication, without mention of misadventure at time of procedure since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other specified procedures as the cause of abnormal reaction of patient, or of later complication, without mention of misadventure at time of procedure' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 AND datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T2.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: Fetch the top four most frequent procedures that were administered to patients within 2 months after they had continuous invasive mechanical ventilation for 96 consecutive hours or more since 2100.

question: What are the five most frequently given lab tests for patients that were diagnosed with dislocation of jaw, initial encounter previously during the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'dislocation of jaw, initial encounter' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )
generated_sql: SELECT TOP 5 LabName, COUNT(*) AS Occurrences FROM PatientLabTests INNER JOIN Patients ON PatientLabTests.PatientID = Patients.ID WHERE Patients.Diagnosis LIKE '%dislocation of jaw, initial encounter%' AND PatientLabTests.TestDate >= DATEADD(YEAR, -1, GETDATE()) GROUP BY LabName ORDER BY Occurrences DESC

question: What are the four most commonly tested specimens for patients who were diagnosed with other fluid overload previously within 2 months, since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T3.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT T2.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other fluid overload' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.spec_type_desc ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: Get me the top four most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed in the same month after being diagnosed with accidental cut, puncture, perforation or hemorrhage during heart catheterization in 2100.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'accidental cut, puncture, perforation or hemorrhage during heart catheterization' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4
generated_sql: SELECT drugs.name, COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM patients JOIN diagnoses ON patients.id = diagnoses.patient_id JOIN drug_prescriptions ON patients.id = drug_prescriptions.patient_id WHERE diagnoses.icd_code LIKE 'I25.2%' AND drug_prescriptions.prescription_date BETWEEN '2000-01-01' AND '2000-12-31' GROUP BY drugs.name ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 4

question: Show me the top five most commonly prescribed drugs during the same hospital encounter to the patients aged 40s after diagnosed with epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus.
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5
generated_sql: SELECT drug_name, COUNT(*) AS occurrences FROM encounters JOIN medications ON encounters.encounter_id = medications.encounter_id JOIN patients ON encounters.patient_id = patients.patient_id WHERE patients.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 AND encounters.diagnosis = 'Epilepsy, unspecified, not intractable, without status epilepticus' GROUP BY drug_name ORDER BY occurrences DESC LIMIT 5

question: Show me the top three diagnoses with the highest 3-month mortality rate.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )
generated_sql: SELECT d.name AS Diagnosis, SUM(CASE WHEN m.status = 'Died' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS Mortality_Rate FROM diagnoses AS d INNER JOIN patient_diagnoses AS pd ON d.id = pd.diagnosis_id INNER JOIN patients AS p ON pd.patient_id = p.id INNER JOIN medical_records AS m ON p.id = m.patient_id WHERE m.timestamp >= NOW() - INTERVAL '3 MONTH' GROUP BY d.name ORDER BY Mortality_Rate DESC LIMIT 3

question: How many days have passed since patient 10004733 had the last alanine aminotransferase (alt) lab test in the current hospital encounter?

question: In 2100, what are the top three most frequent medications prescribed within the same hospital visit to the patients in their 60 or above after they were diagnosed with other ascites?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other ascites' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE admissions.age >= 60 AND strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3
generated_sql: SELECT T1.medication , COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM hospital_visits AS T1 JOIN diagnoses AS T2 ON T1.visit_id = T2.visit_id JOIN patients AS T3 ON T1.patient_id = T3.patient_id WHERE YEAR(T1.visit_date) = 2100 AND T3.age >= 60 AND T2.diagnosis = 'Other ascites' GROUP BY T1.medication ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 3
